name: "I'm fine" by Cinthia Ponce
description:
I always smile like it's nothing, and I always say "I'm fine," but I can see me. I can see how I'm crying my heart out.
After turning off the lights in my silent room, I slowly wither away from what I had been smiling so brightly. In this empty space with no one else sometimes comes a long sigh in the night.

Image source: pexels
Intervention, customization and collage of images. Conceptual art.
With different editing tools.
